# PR size

- **One concern per PR**: e.g. “intake prefill fix” separate from “VMS docx mapping” separate from “cursor rules”.
- If a change touches >15 files or multiple features, split into stacked or sequential PRs.
- Follow `.cursor/rules/git-pr-workflow.mdc` for every merge to `main`.

Large refactors need a short plan in the PR body before review.
